守恒流为，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
J_{\mu}=\sum_{n}\frac{\partial\mathcal{L}}{\partial(\partial_{\mu}\phi_{n})}\frac{\delta\phi_{n}}{\delta\alpha}={\color{red}-i(\phi\partial_{\mu}\phi^{*}-\phi^{*}\partial_{\mu}\phi)}-2eA_{\mu}\phi^{*}\phi
\]

\end_inset

